text: Adam Sedlák (born 21 September 1991) is a Czech ice hockey defenceman currently playing for Orli Znojmo of the Austrian Hockey League (EBEL). He joined Znojmo from HC '05 Banská Bystrica of the Slovak Tipsport liga. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Asiago Hockey 1935 players Category:HC '05 Banská Bystrica players Category:Czech ice hockey defencemen Category:Ducs de Dijon players Category:HC Vítkovice players Category:Knoxville Ice Bears (SPHL) players Category:Living people Category:Orli Znojmo players Category:Ottawa 67's players Category:Peterborough Petes (ice hockey) players Category:SønderjyskE Ishockey players
